title: My 10 Books - September 2013 (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 10 diverse books, all in PDF format with OCR & covers:

01. Adulting - How to Become a Grown-up in 468 Easy(ish) Steps
02. Band-Aid for a Broken Leg
03. Being a Historian - An Introduction to the Professional World of History
04. Craving - Why We Can't Seem to Get Enough
05. Looking for Rights in All the Wrong Places
06. Strange Medicine - A Shocking History of Real Medical Practices Through the Ages
07. The First 20 Hours - How to Learn Anything . . . Fast!
08. The Perilous West
09. The Riddle of the Labyrinth - The Quest to Crack an Ancient Code
10. Winter Gardening in the Maritime Northwest
